OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA murky start with extensive
OL,6,Flow cloud, although cloud tending to
OL,7,Flift slowly into the afternoon, with a
OL,8,Fchance of some limited bright
OL,9,Fintervals developing later inland.
OL,10,FMilder than on Saturday for most,
OL,11,Fespecially where any brighter skies.
OL,12,FLight winds.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FCloud tending to lower
OL,15,Fovernight with mist, patchy fog and
OL,16,Fhill fog becoming more widespread
OL,17,Fagain. Winds remaining generally light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
